rComments: This is the first course I've ever had in a university. Reza farzi makes every part of the chapter very easy to understand, and he always gives you a high grade. I enjoy his lecture so much!!!!

Reza is a model teacher! My standard for good teachers has been raised due to him! Everyone would benefit from taking class with him. He tries to get to know his students which is nice as it added an extra layer to online learning
The only thing that makes this course hard is online class while he couldn't finish a chapter or even slides in class.

Professor Farzi is really a passionate teacher. He adapted perfectly to online teaching. He is really inspirational. I loved his class. In the future, I would choose a class solely because it would be taught by him, whatever the class, it sure would be awesome!!

Professor Reza is really great. There are so many international students taking ESL courses, Reza's English pronunciation is very clear, non-English speakers could follow him easily. He will guide you to learn and there is only a limited amount of homework.

He's lecture is understandable and funny. Online assignment is needed but it is not difficult. Exams are not difficult but you need to prepare for it. You can find him easily in the office he is kind and willing to solve your problems.

Reza is an amazing teacher and he really embodies a great example of how we as inspiring teachers should conduct ourselves. He engages very well with his students and he also teaches them crucial course material that will greatly benefit them in their future career path
Great prof, I will definitely take this course again.

Reza is an absolutely fantastic prof, probably the best prof I have had to date. I had him twice this semester and I am excited to have him again next semester. Genuine prof that really cares about your success, if you do the readings and come to the lectures the class is an easy A.
Mr Farzi is the best teacher ever. He is kind and knowledgable. He helped me improve my language skills. His classes aren't boring at all.

VERY GREAT TEACHER, IF YOU TAKE HIS CLASS, IT WILL NOT BE BORING. HE IS A SERIOUS MAN, BUT HE ALSO LIKES JOKES SOMETIMES. HE LIKES TO GIVE HIS STUDENTS MANY HOMEWORK, PAPERS, ASSIGNMENTS, BUT THESE ARE ALL GOOD FOR YOUR STUDY. BEST TEACHER EVER!!!
Awesome teacher! I wish I could have him as a professor for every class !
Reza is an exellent teacher as he always guide you to succeed in ESL. He is hilarious, helpful and awesome. I honestly learned a lot and I never got bored.
Awesome teacher. He always have time to listen to you. I honestly recommend  course with this professor.
He is one of the best profs if not the best at all I have ever taken english class with. You will definitely improve your english skills at a variety of ways.

Reza is a really hilarious teacher. You rarely feel boring during his class. Most importantly, he is really responsible and helpful teacher! If you want to not just pass this course and also make a huge progress on English, he is definitely most appropriate pro to choose!
He is really helpful, a very kind teacher tough marker but u will certainly benefit from him
